{"tid":1924364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一天即腰斬  希臘奧委會取消當地餘下聖火傳遞","createTime":"2020-03-13T15:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T01:38:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"edd390ad91e402c5a1218286ba7658c2e879ba20","tid":1924364,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"古代奧運發源地、希臘奧林匹亞市周四（12日）舉行聖火採集儀式，並展開東京奧運聖火傳遞，但希臘奧委會周五（13日）公布，因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，取消希臘國內餘下的聖火傳遞，但下周四（19日）聖火會如期在雅典移交日本，屆時將沒有觀眾在場。<br />\n<br />\n希臘奧委會稱，由於聖火傳遞，在伯羅奔尼撒半島（Peloponnese）南部城鎮斯巴達（Sparta）意外地引來大量群眾聚集，迫使奧委會諮詢衛生局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200313/s00005/1584109829761/希臘奧委會取消當地餘下聖火傳遞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200313%2Fs00005%2F1584109829761%2F%E5%B8%8C%E8%87%98%E5%A5%A7%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E9%A4%98%E4%B8%8B%E8%81%96%E7%81%AB%E5%82%B3%E9%81%9E&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=3e0fb597\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200313%2Fs00005%2F1584109829761%2F%E5%B8%8C%E8%87%98%E5%A5%A7%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E9%A4%98%E4%B8%8B%E8%81%96%E7%81%AB%E5%82%B3%E9%81%9E&h=924ddc24\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200313/s00005/1584109829761/希臘奧委會取消當地餘下聖火傳遞</a>"},{"pid":"57b907f562cd882f7280c501a91672a98bdcef89","tid":1924364,"uid":112622,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"879c4ecc6bdd9f0e70b9afe0a6634a2f41e07a83","tid":1924364,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"啲病毒跟住個火炬傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eaf5f2dae9c8faeae0af39667c335c0a1a58307","tid":1924364,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020